de.erichseifert.gral.plots

Class PiePlot.PiePlotNavigator

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.erichseifert.gral.navigation.AbstractNavigator
      • de.erichseifert.gral.plots.PiePlot.PiePlotNavigator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NavigationListener, Navigator
    Enclosing class:
    PiePlot

    public static class PiePlot.PiePlotNavigator
extends AbstractNavigator
    Navigator implementation for pie plots. Zooming changes the RADIUS setting and panning the CENTER setting.
